messages.subject: A Virus Was Sent Out
messages.msgSnippet: When I opened my email this morning, Nortons found a virus. It was able to repair the file, but I wanted everyone to know. This is Nortons information on this
messages.messageBody:
When I opened my email this morning, Nortons found a virus. It was
able to repair the file, but I wanted everyone to know.

This is Nortons information on this virus.

Date: 4/30/02, Time: 9:37:20
The file C:\WINDOWS\TEMP\NAV4083.TMP is infected with the
W32.Badtrans@... virus.
The file was repaired.

This virus was sent to me by a user on this list. I will send that
person a personal message as well. I just wanted everyone here to
know that it happend. If you have a virus program running, make sure
it is up to date. I know in the past I have been hit hard by a virus.
I don't know what this one will do, but they are never a good thing...

Funny thing, my girls and I were just watching on the Discovery
Channel about Allergies, it talked a lot of Virus and antibodies...
Guess Nortons is my computers antibody... :)

Let me know if you need any more information on this one.

Rebecca
